node.text: Who else has been riding the struggle bus with their nails since quarantine? 😂🙋‍♀️I started using press-on nails & I've been obsessed! These press-ons from @glamnetic are EVERYTHING! They are made for comfortable, everyday wear. They're thin and tapered so they look so beautiful on my nails. Don't get me started on the glue, that stuff is stronger than most relationships nowadays😂 I am used to press-on nails popping on pretty quick, but these have survived cleaning, cooking, diaper changes, heavy lifting and more. Get 15% off yours using my code NAZANIN! I am wearing the style Cloud 9 ☁️ #glamnetic #ad

node.text:
As a mother, all this new info on child sex trafficking is absolutely disturbing and terrifying. I’ve teamed up with these amazing influencers to #jointhefight and work with @childrescuecoalition which is an amazing nonprofit organization that locates IP addresses of abusers who upload/download sexually explicit images of underage children. 

Our goal is to raise $100k for this organization and NEED YOUR HELP! We are asking you to donate $10 to help us reach this goal. If you are unable to donate, that’s completely okay! Please share on your social media accounts, with your friends and family, and help us spread the word. Join us in this fight today and let’s amplify the voices of these innocent children. Donation link is on my story🤍

node.text:
Happy Sunday ☀️ here’s my look from my last YT video! Had fun playing with some color 🤍
• @dominiquecosmetics x @jadeywadey180 primer 
• @lancomeofficial foundation in 260N 
• @elfcosmetics hydrating concealer in light peach 
• @maybelline fit me concealer in Cafe
• @hudabeauty easy bake powder in Cupcake 
• @buxomcosmetics bronzer in Rooftop Tan 
• @anastasiabeverlyhills brow wiz in Taupe 
• @plouise_makeup_academy base
• @bhcosmetics Avocado Toast Palette (Shades Avo Toast, Pit, Avocuddle, Lemon Pepper, Holy Moly)
• @lillylashes Liner Adhesive, Lashes in Miami Flare (code naz10 for $$$ off)
• @hudabeauty mascara 
• @bhcosmetics Bellini Blush Palette 
• @anastasiabeverlyhills x @amrezy Highlighter 
• @maccosmetics Cork Lip Liner 
• @maybelline superstay ink in Driver
• @buxomcosmetics glows in White Russian Sparkle 
• @itcosmetics hydrating setting spray

Song: They Call Me Tiago by @iamtiagz 
—————————————————
#maybelline #hudabeauty #lancome #maccosmetics #anastasiabeverlyhills #bhcosmetics #buxom #itcosmetics #lillylashes #makeup

node.text:
My at home blowout routine 💕I do this routine on wash day and my hair stays styled ALL week🙌🏼 here’s how I do it + all my fave products to use!

I didn’t show this on camera but it’s SO important to have a clean scalp for this look. Excess oil will just weigh your hair down & make it harder to have that fluffy 90s look. I used my @prose Clarifying shampoo + my scalp massager in the shower 🚿 

I sprayed my hair with my @kenraprofessional Blow-Dry AP and detangled using my @denmanbrush! This Mist is everything 😍 not only does it work as a heat protectant, but it helps my hair dry so quick! 

Then I use my @olaplex No. 6 Bond Smoother! This is the ultimate blow dry cream 🙌🏼 a little goes a long way… I used a little too much in this video but I have thick hair so it was able to handle it 😂 it also smells so good 

I then take my @conair blow dryer and just dry my roots! This is very helpful when using a blowdry brush because they’re too big to really smooth your roots (especially if you have curly hair)

My Blow Dry brush is from @revlon but I have one from different brands & they all work great! I just make sure to keep rotating the brush to get that curl at the bottom 

I finish off using my @olaplex No. 7 bonding oil to smooth flyaways & add some shine 💫

node.text:
5-mins to do my makeup?? No problem 💅these products from @uomabysharonc got me 🙌🏼 #UOMAbysharonC is a vegan, cruelty free, black-owned beauty brand NOW available @walmart! 
Their Flawless IRL foundation is EVERYTHING 😍I’m in the shade Honey Honey
I also used the It’s Complicated stain in the shade Peng on my cheeks, eyes, and lips for a quick monochromatic look🤍
#5minglowup #BySharonC #UOMABeauty
